</font> </b> </div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 163<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/14/02 7:54:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=203.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What would make you want to use a shield?</span><hr size=1> Varner has my idea exactly...<br>
<br>
The Block Skill, tied to the use of a Shield, would make a Shield very valuable.<br>
<br>
Cap the skill at 75-100, then put Shields in the game with +10% or +20% to Block... and maybe procs on shields as well.<br>
<br>
